<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Studio Neoansa | Katalog Seni</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #111;
      color: #ddd;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #000, #222);
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: #f0f0f0;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    header p {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      color: #aaa;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #f5f5f5;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #555;
      display: inline-block;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .gallery {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 25px;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .card {
      background-color: #1b1b1b;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px #000;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
    }

    .card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 220px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 15px 0 5px;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #aaa;
      padding: 0 15px 10px;
    }

    .whatsapp-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 10px auto 20px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      background-color: #25d366;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .whatsapp-btn:hover {
      background-color: #1ebe5d;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #111;
      color: #777;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #333;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Studio Neoansa</h1>
    <p>Menghidupkan kembali budaya dan seni melalui karya Diorama, Patung, dan Figuratif Art. 
    Setiap karya kami adalah bentuk penghormatan terhadap nilai estetika dan tradisi yang menginspirasi.</p>
  </header>

  <section id="diorama">
    <h2>Diorama</h2>
    <div class="gallery">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/600x400/?diorama,art" alt="Diorama 1">
        <h3>Diorama Tradisional</h3>
        <p>Miniatur pemandangan budaya lokal yang penuh detail dan makna.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6287759782958" class="whatsapp-btn">Pesan via WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/600x400/?miniature,sculpture" alt="Diorama 2">
        <h3>Diorama Sejarah</h3>
        <p>Menceritakan kisah masa lalu lewat karya tiga dimensi yang hidup.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6287759782958" class="whatsapp-btn">Pesan via WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="patung">
    <h2>Patung</h2>
    <div class="gallery">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/600x400/?sculpture,art" alt="Patung 1">
        <h3>Patung Klasik</h3>
        <p>Dibentuk dengan kehalusan dan ketelitian, menampilkan keanggunan budaya.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6287759782958" class="whatsapp-btn">Pesan via WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/600x400/?statue,handmade" alt="Patung 2">
        <h3>Patung Modern</h3>
        <p>Perpaduan seni klasik dan ekspresi kontemporer dalam satu karya unik.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6287759782958" class="whatsapp-btn">Pesan via WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="figuratif">
    <h2>Figuratif Art</h2>
    <div class="gallery">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/600x400/?figurative,art" alt="Figuratif 1">
        <h3>Ekspresi Jiwa</h3>
        <p>Visualisasi manusia dan budaya dalam harmoni warna dan bentuk.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6287759782958" class="whatsapp-btn">Pesan via WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/600x400/?art,painting" alt="Figuratif 2">
        <h3>Seni Naratif</h3>
        <p>Menceritakan kisah dan emosi lewat goresan penuh makna.</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6287759782958" class="whatsapp-btn">Pesan via WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    © 2025 Studio Neoansa — Karya Seni dan Budaya Indonesia
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
